{"tid":1566156,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人月兩團圓","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:59:09.000Z","uid":182477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1764bbcb1dc3fa59c5ca5c759577dc71d141459","tid":1566156,"uid":182477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"一年前既中秋節與一年後既中秋節 <br />\n我們由同一星球的人 變成了分開億萬里的人<br />\n<br />\n人有無窮無盡既慾望 想要得到亦會失去<br />\n以前我不願付出 不願體諒 不願感激的人 <br />\n今天成為我的遺憾 以前我以爲你永遠屬於我<br />\n原來我自私 我既冷漠 影響了大家對大家既愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為現在我真的很愛你<br />\n我願意離開你視線 不再影響你的感受<br />\n因為現在的你遠比以前的你開心 快樂<br />\n如果我去打破你的保護網 等於奪走你的氧氣<br />\n<br />\n現在我只需要作為你朋友 去關心你 去了解你<br />\n幫你留意一下你喜愛的事 給你一些資訊<br />\n希望可以幫你分擔一點一點 不論結果<br />\n<br />\n當我有能力去證明自己的時候 <br />\n我會穿越保護網去嘗試接觸你 <br />\n現在的你不作任何回應是對我們最好的方法<br />\n<br />\n我很愛你 我願意以我現在 換取一個不可能的機會<br />\n<br />\nGuardian!"},{"pid":"0ec14745c9a7ba466b1847ed93d8e21ea3b58a17","tid":1566156,"uid":162422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"Mk"},{"pid":"dd1ec80942fac3e773b384004e1934c5ddf3483e","tid":1566156,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}